item.title: Example Of Notebook Conversion
item.description: Metatab has it’s own Notebook conversion process, will will create a Metatab package with the notebook, it’s Makrdown and HTML conversion, and the dataset it creates. FOr these conversions, input code cells are by default hidden and must be explicitly re-enabled by starting code cells with %showinput The Notebook can include inline Metatab, in a line-oriented format. These cells are code cells and start with a %%metatab magic. %%metatab Identifier: override_this Identifier: this_one_too Identifier: 7108517a-7163-41a5-943d-961f9a086a3f Origin: example.
